commit.title: [feedback] Add phase attribute.
commit.message:
[feedback] Add phase attribute.

This is an alternative to #8789; I was not very happy with the
solution that we provided there, it seems wrong to mask the feeder
itself in order to reflect modal information.

This patch is not perfect either, but I do wonder what the best
trade-off would be here.
